						<a class="post_more_title" href="https://lithub.com/ghetto-koans-pattern-books-devouring-wolves-seven-poetry-collections-to-read-in-july/">
				<h4 style="margin:0">Ghetto Koans, Pattern Books, Devouring Wolves: Seven Poetry Collections to Read in July</h4>
			</a>
			As I write this introduction, there’s a heatwave and the world is a mess. As we watch the defunding of many of the institutions...			
			</div>
